#### Fixing Missing Data

The highest elevation of any weather station in this dataset is 4113 meters above mean sea level.[^1]

[^1]: Units and measurement pulled from the dataset's data dictionary: `met-datadictionary.pdf`

```{r}
met$elev[met$elev==9999.0] <- NA
summary(met$elev)

met <- met[met$temp > -40, ]
met2 <- met[order(met$temp), ]
head(met2)
```

### 5 - Checking the data

```{r}
met <- met[met$temp>-15, ]
met2 <- met[order(met$temp), ]
head(met2)
```

### 6 - **Summary statistics**

```{r}
elev <- met[met$elev==max(met$elev, na.rm=TRUE), ]
summary(elev)

cor(elev$temp, elev$wind.sp, use="complete")
cor(elev$temp, elev$hour, use="complete")
cor(elev$wind.sp, elev$day, use="complete")
cor(elev$wind.sp, elev$hour, use="complete")
cor(elev$temp, elev$day, use="complete")
```

